{"tid":2014811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嗰啲係咁話要保留海洋公園嘅人係咪傻鳩？","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T00:40:56.000Z","uid":28114,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54560806782a3dcd412652c742892f622db292ee","tid":2014811,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"海洋公園喺盛智民年代叻極都係平均賺一億一年。而依家未注資50億嘅情況下預計十年後海洋公園欠債80億，即係再借嘅話舉債超過100億。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當你未來大賺叻過盛智民一年賺2億，未計利息都要還50年！！！</span>無疑係一個財政黑洞。<br />\n<br />\n一門咁嘅生意、咁嘅業績，問世上任何一見銀行都唔會借。試問你拎啲乜嘢出嚟抵押呢？<br />\n<br />\nPS 2018/19年海洋公園年總收入17億，虧損5.5億 （即係一年開支22億幾）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100004429423231/posts/1559760340848265/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100004429423231%2Fposts%2F1559760340848265%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=94f9fdc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100004429423231/posts/1559760340848265/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"382cf64132a008b81aff5c3a946496dd82e74b83","tid":2014811,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe2f51fd520c41f817ff52409442d6875c91a4f","tid":2014811,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"啲人淨係留負皮<br />\n<br />\n但係又駁唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef64c3793fdabea9865967cf9cd132dee0f9a30","tid":2014811,"uid":258770,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"唔係想撐海洋公園<br />\n係想反對將會取代海洋公園既野<br />\n講真我好似正係去過一次 可能呢一世都唔會再去<br />\n但有個濕鳩公園點都好過豪宅軍營之類"},{"pid":"d3286649627dff6a4d6e555bf38dbd973253e802","tid":2014811,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"